*   **[Defined contribution](/Defined_contribution_plan)**: What you get is what you put in, and what the market allows. A gamble, really.
*   **[Pay-as-you-go](/Pay-as-you-go_pension_plan)**: The current generation pays for the previous one. A Ponzi scheme with good intentions.
